{"tid":1992175,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Steam 將台灣、香港列為「國家」：何以小粉紅腳都震","createTime":"2020-04-28T03:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T13:09:14.000Z","uid":105567,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"652971a62e1604cde69217f0ab67e6720d8107fc","tid":1992175,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.fanpiece.com/GM5HPcm?page=fanpiece\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.fanpiece.com%2FGM5HPcm%3Fpage%3Dfanpiece&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPhUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=7ca1996a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.fanpiece.com/GM5HPcm?page=fanpiece</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲界近年向中国叩頭不少，偏偏Steam就將台灣、香港、藏南劃出中國領土，作為國家之列，正常的發揮，應該是「小粉紅聲討--&gt;中国政府封禁」是吧？但今次偏偏一反常態。<br />\n<br />\n莫講話劃區，先前中國政府多次吹雞「全國哀悼」、「整改」時都Steam完全沒有跟從，原因很簡單：除了特別劃分的中國專區「Steam China」讓中国開發者與審查方圍爐，其他伺服器都從來當中国政府冇到。<br />\n<br />\n然而小粉紅今次一反常態異常忍手，不敢聲張，因為Steam上的遊戲太不可替代，而且中国用戶人達超過三千萬人，是世界主流遊戲平台中僅餘能夠讓中国玩家與文明世界用戶共存的「最後防線」。<br />\n<br />\n最近《動森》系列於中国伺服器，因為領導一聲起意就全滅，令到一直囂張的中国玩家開始出現危機感，發覺即使本身十分中性無害的合家歡遊戲原來也是審查制服的眼線之下，但當然，他們只會卑微哀求，從不維權。<br />\n<br />\n今次Steam出招，有中国玩家跪到腳震地求饒，盡顯奴才本色。<br />\n[attachimg]11082624[/attachimg] [attachimg]11082625[/attachimg] <br />\n<br />\n至被屈是《動森》封禁「禍首」的黃之鋒，當然「送佢地一程」，更抵死地以極度中国的留言方式落井下石，用力抽水誓要將他們「牛逼死」為止，但今次小粉紅恐怕連「NMSL」都不敢N一聲了。"},{"pid":"f992f18091630b84979760ff77adc4b6bfbbbb32","tid":1992175,"uid":105567,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPrmsve.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPrmsve.png&h=9d444011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSHEeag.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSHEeag.png&h=d90b896c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1a12534df209043a63a199c88383bdb9f7c588a","tid":1992175,"uid":41414,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"我係每隻買既遊戲都留言武漢肺炎 <br />\n<br />\n習近平 小熊維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f056960c6f41b12e978546d434424af659ba5e","tid":1992175,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20268eef2824d9cb0f841cd23d4354beebd60817","tid":1992175,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"nmsl<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}